ğŸš¨ ABSOLUTE RED FLAGS (STOP IMMEDIATELY)::::::::::

âŒ Seller shows only photocopies
âŒ EC missing mortgage entry explanation
âŒ Plot not in approved layout
âŒ No CLU for residential land
âŒ Seller avoids mutation
âŒ No bank NOC despite loan history
âŒ Boundary mismatch


â“ First Questions to Ask the Seller (Short & Practical)::::::::::

Is the plot FREEHOLD?
Are you the sole owner? (Any co-owner / heir?)
Can you show the ORIGINAL sale deed chain (15â€“20 yrs)?
Any loan or mortgage ever taken on this plot? (Bank NOC?)
Is the land use RESIDENTIAL? (Approved layout / CLU?)
Is mutation done in your name?
Any dues pending? (Property tax, society, GDA?)
Any dispute, notice, or court case?
Is road access approved and clear?
Why are you selling? (Listen carefully)

